msgstr "tipkovnica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "This module allows you to choose how your keyboard works."
msgstr "Ta modul vam omogoča izbiro načina delovanja vaše tipkovnice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are three tabs in this module."
msgstr "V tem modulu so trije zavihki."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Hardware tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Strojna oprema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actual effect of setting these options depends upon the features "
"provided by your keyboard hardware and the X server on which &plasma; is "
"running. As an example, you may find that changing the key click volume has "
"no effect because that feature is not available on your system."
msgstr ""
"Dejanski učinek nastavitve teh možnosti je odvisen od funkcij, ki jih "
"zagotavljata strojna oprema tipkovnice in strežnik X, v katerem se izvaja "
"program &plasma;. Na primer, lahko ugotovite, da sprememba glasnosti klika "
"tipke nima učinka, ker ta funkcija v vašem sistemu ni na voljo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard model:"
msgstr "Model tipkovnice:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can set your keyboard model. This setting is independent of your "
"keyboard layout and refers to the &quot;hardware&quot; model, &ie; the way "
"your keyboard is manufactured. Modern keyboards that come with your computer "
"usually have two extra keys and are referred to as &quot;104-key&quot; "
"models, which is probably what you want if you do not know what kind of "
"keyboard you have."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko nastavite model tipkovnice. Ta nastavitev je neodvisna od "
"razporeditve tipkovnice in se nanaša na model &quot;strojne opreme&quot;, "
"&ie; na način izdelave tipkovnice. Sodobne tipkovnice, ki so priložene "
"računalniku, imajo običajno dve dodatni tipki, znane kot &quot;104-tipka "
"&quot; modeli, kar je verjetno tisto, kar želite, če ne veste, kakšno "
"tipkovnico imate."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "NumLock on Plasma Startup"
msgstr "NumLock ob zagonu Plasma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to either always <guilabel>Turn on</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Turn off</guilabel> the NumLock when &plasma; starts, or you can "
"choose to have &plasma; leave NumLock at whatever it was set to before "
"&plasma; started up."
msgstr ""
"Izbirate lahko med <guilabel>Vklopi</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Izklopi</"
"guilabel>, da vklopite /izklopite NumLock ob zagonu &plasma; ali pa "
"izberete, da boste pustili NumLock na vrednosti, kakršni je bil, preden je "
"bil &plasma; zagnan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "When a key is held:"
msgstr "Ko držite tipko:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is possible to select one of the tree options here, namely"
msgstr "Tu lahko izberete eno od treh možnosti drevesa, in sicer"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show accented and similar characters"
msgstr "Prikaži naglašene in podobne znake"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, when a key is held down while entering text, a "
"popup is shown which lets one choose between various accented forms of the "
"character."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost izbrana, se ob pritisnjeni tipki med vnašanjem besedila "
"prikaže pojavno okno, ki omogoča izbiro med različnimi naglašenimi oblikami "
"znaka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do nothing"
msgstr "Ne stori ničesar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to turn off any activities when you pressing and "
"holding down the keys."
msgstr ""
"S to možnostjo lahko izklopite vse dejavnosti, ko pritisnete in držite tipke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Repeat the key"
msgstr "Ponovi tipko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this option is selected, pressing and holding down a key emits the same "
"character repeatedly until the key is released. Pressing and holding the key "
"will have the same effect as pressing it multiple times in succession."
msgstr ""
"Kadar je izbrana ta možnost pritisk in držanje tipke ponavlja enak znak "
"dokler ni tipka spuščena. Pritisk in držanje tipke bo imel enak učinek kot "
"večkratno zaporedno pritiskanje tipke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Almost all users will want to have this option enabled, because it makes "
"navigating through documents with the arrow keys significantly easier."
msgstr ""
"To možnost bodo želeli imeti vključeno skoraj vsi uporabniki, saj precej "
"olajša gibanje skozi dokumente s pomočjo puščičnih tipk."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delay"
msgstr "Zakasnitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to set the delay after which a pressed key will start "
"generating keycodes."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost omogoča nastavitev zakasnitve, po kateri bo pritisnjena tipka "
"začela ustvarjati kode tipk."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rate"
msgstr "Hitrost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option allows you to set the rate at which keycodes are generated while "
"a key is pressed."
msgstr ""
"S to možnostjo lahko nastavite hitrost, s katero se generirajo kode tipk, ko "
"je tipka pritisnjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type some characters into the <guilabel>Test area</guilabel> text box to "
"verify the settings."
msgstr ""
"V besedilno polje <guilabel>Testno območje</guilabel> vnesite nekaj znakov "
"in preverite nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Many computers won't support this function."
msgstr "Mnogo računalnikov ne bo podpiralo te funkcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Layouts tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Postavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab lets you choose what keyboard layouts you want to use, what "
"indicator you want in the system tray, how you want to switch and which "
"shortcuts you will use."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku lahko izberete, katere postavitve tipkovnice želite "
"uporabljati, kateri indikator želite v sistemski vrstici, kako želite "
"preklapljati in katere bližnjice boste uporabljali."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Layout Indicator"
msgstr "Indikator postavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose to <guilabel>Show layout indicator</guilabel> which will show "
"the language iso name in the system tray. You can choose to show the "
"indicator even if you have a single layout enabled and you can show the "
"language flag instead of only the ISO code by checking <guilabel>Show flag</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko možnost <guilabel>Pokaži indikator postavitve</guilabel>, ki "
"bo v sistemski vrstici prikazala ime jezikovnega iso. Kazalnik lahko "
"prikažete tudi, če je omogočena ena sama postavitev, in z izbiro možnosti "
"<guilabel>Pokaži zastavico</guilabel> lahko prikažete zastavico jezika in ne "
"le kodo ISO."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Policy"
msgstr "Politika preklapljanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you select <guilabel>Application</guilabel> or <guilabel>Window</"
"guilabel> switching policy, changing the keyboard layout will only affect "
"the current application or window. <guilabel>Global</guilabel> will change "
"the keyboard layout globally and <guilabel>Desktop</guilabel> will change it "
"only for the current virtual desktop."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete politiko preklapljanja <guilabel>Aplikacija</guilabel> ali "
"<guilabel>Okno</guilabel>, bo sprememba postavitve tipkovnice vplivala samo "
"na trenutno aplikacijo ali okno. <guilabel>Globalno</guilabel> bo spremenila "
"postavitev tipkovnice globalno, <guilabel>Namizje</guilabel> pa jo bo "
"spremenila samo za trenutno virtualno namizje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcuts for Switching Layout"
msgstr "Bližnjice za preklop postavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Main shortcuts</guilabel> is a shortcut for switching layouts "
"which is handled by X.org. <guilabel>3rd level shortcuts</guilabel> is a "
"shortcut for switching to a third level of the active layout (if it has one) "
"which is handled by X.org. It allows modifier-only shortcuts. "
"<guilabel>Alternative shortcut</guilabel> is a shortcut for switching "
"layouts which is handled by &plasma;. It does not support modifier-only "
"shortcuts and also may not work in some situations (&eg; if popup is active "
"or from screensaver)."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Glavne bližnjice</guilabel> je bližnjica za preklop med "
"postavitvami, ki jo upravlja X.org. <guilabel>3-nadstropne bližnjice</"
"guilabel> je bližnjica za preklop na tretjo raven aktivne postavitve (če jo "
"ima), ki jo upravlja X.org. Omogoča bližnjice samo za modifikatorje. "
"<guilabel>Alternativna bližnjica</guilabel> je bližnjica za preklapljanje "
"postavitev, ki ga upravlja &plasma;. Ne podpira bližnjic, ki imajo samo "
"modifikatorje in v nekaterih primerih morda ne bo delovala (&eg; če je "
"aktivno pojavno okno ali iz ohranjevalnika zaslona)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure layouts"
msgstr "Konfiguracija postavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check <guilabel>Configure layouts</guilabel> you will be able to add "
"and remove keyboard layouts in order to switch between them when you need."
msgstr ""
"Če označite možnost <guilabel>Konfiguriracija postavitev</guilabel>, boste "
"lahko dodajali in odstranjevali postavitve tipkovnice, da boste lahko po "
"potrebi preklapljali med njimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on <guibutton>Add</guibutton> will open a dialog where you will be "
"able to choose the new keyboard layout you want to add as well as its "
"variant, label and shortcut."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> se odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"lahko izberete novo postavitev tipkovnice, ki jo želite dodati, ter njeno "
"različico, oznako in bližnjico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The list of layouts right to the <guilabel>Layout</guilabel> label in the "
"<guilabel>Add Layout</guilabel> dialog can be narrowed down using "
"<guilabel>Limit selection by language</guilabel> drop-down list. You can "
"click on <guibutton>Preview</guibutton> button to preview chosen layout in a "
"separate window."
msgstr ""
"Seznam postavitev, ki se nahaja tik ob oznaki <guilabel>Postavitev</"
"guilabel> v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Dodaj postavitev</guilabel>, lahko "
"zožite z uporabo spustnega seznama <guilabel>Omejiti izbiro po jeziku</"
"guilabel>. S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Predogled</guibutton> si lahko "
"izbrano postavitev ogledate v ločenem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can order the layouts with the up and down buttons, the top one being "
"the default one."
msgstr ""
"Postavitve lahko uredite s tipkama za navzgor in navzdol, pri čemer je "
"zgornja postavitev privzeta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spare layouts"
msgstr "Rezervne postavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option can be enabled only if you have more than two layouts."
msgstr "To možnost lahko omogočite le, če imate več kot dve postavitvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Spare layouts allow to toggle between small number of layouts easily while "
"keeping more layouts handy close by. For example you might use 3 languages: "
"English, Ukrainian and German but first two are used often and third one "
"just occasionally. In this case you can configure first two as main layouts "
"(setting <guilabel>Main layout count</guilabel>: 2) and German one as spare "
"one - when you toggle with keyboard and left mouse button the switch will "
"happen between main layouts only but you can always choose 3rd layout with "
"context menu."
msgstr ""
"Z rezervnimi postavitvami lahko preprosto preklapljate med majhnim številom "
"postavitev, hkrati pa imate več postavitev pri roki. Uporabljate lahko na "
"primer tri jezike: angleščino, ukrajinščino in nemščino, vendar prva dva "
"uporabljate pogosto, tretjega pa le občasno. V tem primeru lahko prvi dve "
"nastavite kot glavni postavitvi (nastavitev <guilabel>Število glavnih "
"postavitev</guilabel>: 2), nemško pa kot rezervno - ko preklapljate s "
"tipkovnico in levim gumbom miške, se bo preklopil samo med glavnima "
"postavitvama, vendar lahko vedno izberete tretjo postavitev s kontekstnim "
"menijem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When spare layout is chosen it replaces the last main layout (this is done "
"for technical reasons, usually global shortcuts work based on the 1st active "
"layout so it's more reliable to preserve the 1st layout when allowing to "
"activate spare layouts)."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana rezervna postavitev, zamenja zadnjo glavno postavitev (to je "
"narejeno iz tehničnih razlogov, običajno globalne bližnjice delujejo na "
"podlagi prve aktivne postavitve, zato je bolj zanesljivo, da se ohrani prva "
"postavitev, ko se omogoči aktiviranje rezervnih postavitev)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As X.org only allows to have 4 layouts to switch <quote>spare layouts</"
"quote> feature also allows to overcome this limitation: user can have up to "
"4 main layouts (managed by X.org) but 4 more spare layouts allowed (managed "
"by layout switcher). Thus user can conveniently work with up to total of 8 "
"layouts (although the 4 spare layouts limit can be raised in the future)."
msgstr ""
"Ker X.org dovoljuje le 4 postavitve za preklapljanje, lahko s funkcijo "
"<quote>proste postavitve</quote> premagate to omejitev: uporabnik ima lahko "
"največ 4 glavne postavitve (ki jih upravlja X.org), dovoljene pa so še 4 "
"proste postavitve (ki jih upravlja stikalo postavitev). Tako lahko uporabnik "
"udobno dela z do 8 postavitvami (čeprav se lahko omejitev 4 rezervnih "
"postavitev v prihodnosti poveča)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Advanced tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Napredno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this tab, if you check <guilabel>Configure keyboard options</guilabel> "
"you will then be able to set a few options regarding some special keys "
"settings. You can expand these options by clicking on the &gt; symbol on the "
"left of the option then you choose your setting in the expanded list."
msgstr ""
"Če v tem zavihku označite možnost <guilabel>Konfiguriranje možnosti "
"tipkovnice</guilabel>, boste lahko nastavili nekaj možnosti glede nekaterih "
"posebnih nastavitev tipk. Te možnosti lahko razširite s klikom na simbol "
"&gt; na levi strani možnosti, nato pa na razširjenem seznamu izberete "
"nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a &GUI; to help creating custom keyboard layouts for &X11; using XKB."
msgstr ""
"To je &GUI; za pomoč pri ustvarjanju poljubnih postavitev tipkovnice za "
"&X11; z uporabo XKB."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information please refer to the <emphasis>Links</emphasis> section "
"on the <ulink url=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/XKeyboardConfig"
"\">XKeyboardConfig page on freedesktop.org</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij glejte razdelek <emphasis>Odnosi</emphasis> na strani "
"<ulink url=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/XKeyboardConfig"
"\">XKeyboardConfig na freedesktop.org</ulink>."

